{"tid":2008660,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"父/母親節反思","createTime":"2020-05-09T07:52:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T07:53:39.000Z","uid":57405,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a69c15826728ea2e7a30b38e789c0619d48610e0","tid":2008660,"uid":57405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:52:15.000Z","msg":"母親節又到，好多人都係Facebook/IG不斷打卡自己會送D咩比阿媽。<br />\n每年父/母親節，好多人都會同人share自己果日點同阿爸阿媽慶祝，又加句咩「多謝阿爸阿媽照顧」呀之類。<br />\n我唔係想叫大家做不孝子不孝女，但其實大家有冇諗過，父/母親節的定立，其實反而係一種歧視?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wfcdaily/videos/638100419589035/UzpfSTE3ODg0OTg2ODg0NzQyODo1MDMxNTQzMzMxMjY1NDU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwfcdaily%2Fvideos%2F638100419589035%2FUzpfSTE3ODg0OTg2ODg0NzQyODo1MDMxNTQzMzMxMjY1NDU%2F&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d8g7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=99bc2f38\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wfcdaily/videos/638100419589035/UzpfSTE3ODg0OTg2ODg0NzQyODo1MDMxNTQzMzMxMjY1NDU/</a><br />\n古天樂係《戀情告急》入面講過，雙方係相愛既，一年365日都係情人節，冇必要2月14先浪漫一次。<br />\n同樣，做仔女，孝順父母係必然。如果大家有心，一年365日都係父/母親節，如果大家只係5月第2個星期同6月第3個星期先孝順父母，又係咪一個孝子/女？"},{"pid":"3c6ebc8a9ba76b2ab486e2a808e13374b4d0ba78","tid":2008660,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T07:53:39.000Z","msg":"中二病<br />\n立意唔明顯<br />\n推論不足"}]}